[{"text": "see the assembly will now hear an", "start": 0.0, "duration": 6.299}, {"text": "address by his Excellency Lazarus", "start": 3.0, "duration": 6.059}, {"text": "McCarthy chuckwara president of the", "start": 6.299, "duration": 4.281}, {"text": "Republic of Malawi and", "start": 9.059, "duration": 4.62}, {"text": "commander-in-chief of the Malawi Defense", "start": 10.58, "duration": 4.84}, {"text": "Force", "start": 13.679, "duration": 4.561}, {"text": "I request protocol to escort his", "start": 15.42, "duration": 5.3}, {"text": "Excellency", "start": 18.24, "duration": 2.48}, {"text": "on behalf of the general assembly I have", "start": 22.26, "duration": 5.279}, {"text": "the honor to welcome his Excellency", "start": 25.14, "duration": 5.299}, {"text": "Lazarus McCarthy", "start": 27.539, "duration": 6.381}, {"text": "president of the Republic of Malawi and", "start": 30.439, "duration": 5.8}, {"text": "commander-in-chief of the Malawi Defense", "start": 33.92, "duration": 5.08}, {"text": "Force and I invite him to address the", "start": 36.239, "duration": 4.98}, {"text": "assembly", "start": 39.0, "duration": 5.28}, {"text": "you're actually insane Mr Dennis Francis", "start": 41.219, "duration": 5.881}, {"text": "president of the seventh eighth session", "start": 44.28, "duration": 5.88}, {"text": "of the United Nations General Assembly", "start": 47.1, "duration": 4.56}, {"text": "Your Excellence seems to Antonio", "start": 50.16, "duration": 3.96}, {"text": "guterres Secretary General of the United", "start": 51.66, "duration": 4.02}, {"text": "Nations", "start": 54.12, "duration": 3.84}, {"text": "your excellencies", "start": 55.68, "duration": 5.1}, {"text": "heads of state and government and", "start": 57.96, "duration": 4.68}, {"text": "leaders of delegations distinguished", "start": 60.78, "duration": 2.88}, {"text": "delegates", "start": 62.64, "duration": 3.479}, {"text": "ladies and gentlemen", "start": 63.66, "duration": 4.98}, {"text": "in less than 30 years", "start": 66.119, "duration": 5.761}, {"text": "we will come to the halfway point", "start": 68.64, "duration": 5.46}, {"text": "of this century", "start": 71.88, "duration": 5.279}, {"text": "and in less than 80 years", "start": 74.1, "duration": 5.699}, {"text": "the 21st century will end", "start": 77.159, "duration": 4.261}, {"text": "by that time", "start": 79.799, "duration": 3.121}, {"text": "none of us", "start": 81.42, "duration": 3.36}, {"text": "will be president", "start": 82.92, "duration": 5.339}, {"text": "and none of us will be alive", "start": 84.78, "duration": 5.879}, {"text": "so when we stand at this podium", "start": 88.259, "duration": 4.621}, {"text": "and speak of the future", "start": 90.659, "duration": 4.561}, {"text": "we speak of a future that does not", "start": 92.88, "duration": 5.46}, {"text": "belong to us", "start": 95.22, "duration": 6.12}, {"text": "we speak of a future with sustainable", "start": 98.34, "duration": 4.56}, {"text": "development", "start": 101.34, "duration": 5.459}, {"text": "we speak of a better world not for us", "start": 102.9, "duration": 7.38}, {"text": "but for our grandchildren and their", "start": 106.799, "duration": 5.401}, {"text": "children", "start": 110.28, "duration": 4.74}, {"text": "and the decisions we make today", "start": 112.2, "duration": 5.82}, {"text": "the actions we take each day", "start": 115.02, "duration": 6.84}, {"text": "are what determine what kind of future", "start": 118.02, "duration": 6.54}, {"text": "we are creating for them", "start": 121.86, "duration": 5.28}, {"text": "it is therefore not good enough", "start": 124.56, "duration": 5.58}, {"text": "to say that we must build trust in the", "start": 127.14, "duration": 4.02}, {"text": "world", "start": 130.14, "duration": 3.3}, {"text": "when we continue making decisions that", "start": 131.16, "duration": 4.62}, {"text": "undermine Trust", "start": 133.44, "duration": 4.74}, {"text": "it is not good enough to say that we", "start": 135.78, "duration": 4.38}, {"text": "want to reignite", "start": 138.18, "duration": 4.32}, {"text": "Global solidarity", "start": 140.16, "duration": 5.579}, {"text": "when we continue to pick and choose", "start": 142.5, "duration": 7.08}, {"text": "whom we show solidarity with", "start": 145.739, "duration": 6.961}, {"text": "it is not enough to say we want to move", "start": 149.58, "duration": 5.4}, {"text": "towards peace", "start": 152.7, "duration": 4.44}, {"text": "when our actions", "start": 154.98, "duration": 4.08}, {"text": "in other nations", "start": 157.14, "duration": 5.04}, {"text": "promote war and create the conditions", "start": 159.06, "duration": 5.58}, {"text": "for conflict", "start": 162.18, "duration": 4.62}, {"text": "it is not good enough", "start": 164.64, "duration": 5.22}, {"text": "to say we want prosperity for all", "start": 166.8, "duration": 5.4}, {"text": "when our rules for trade and our", "start": 169.86, "duration": 5.879}, {"text": "financial systems are a recipe for", "start": 172.2, "duration": 8.52}, {"text": "deepening the poverty of other nations", "start": 175.739, "duration": 7.86}, {"text": "without changing our decisions our", "start": 180.72, "duration": 6.0}, {"text": "positions and our actions", "start": 183.599, "duration": 6.481}, {"text": "the future we speak of today and the", "start": 186.72, "duration": 5.64}, {"text": "sustainable development we dream of", "start": 190.08, "duration": 4.92}, {"text": "achieving by 2030", "start": 192.36, "duration": 4.86}, {"text": "will remain a reality", "start": 195.0, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "on paper", "start": 197.22, "duration": 5.159}, {"text": "and when it comes to Urgent action we", "start": 199.2, "duration": 6.3}, {"text": "must focus our Attention our energies", "start": 202.379, "duration": 7.14}, {"text": "and our resources on the areas where we", "start": 205.5, "duration": 6.9}, {"text": "are falling behind", "start": 209.