961}, {"text": "against sharks", "start": 580.8, "duration": 4.02}, {"text": "we are committed to continue engaging", "start": 582.36, "duration": 4.08}, {"text": "the United Nations", "start": 584.82, "duration": 4.76}, {"text": "under our development Partners both", "start": 586.44, "duration": 6.38}, {"text": "multilaterally as well as bilaterally", "start": 589.58, "duration": 7.0}, {"text": "immobilizing international support that", "start": 592.82, "duration": 6.82}, {"text": "goes beyond disaster management and", "start": 596.58, "duration": 6.12}, {"text": "seeks to build sustainability", "start": 599.64, "duration": 5.46}, {"text": "we are committed to continue banging on", "start": 602.7, "duration": 5.22}, {"text": "the doors of financial institutions", "start": 605.1, "duration": 5.1}, {"text": "that remain too slow and too", "start": 607.92, "duration": 5.28}, {"text": "unresponsive and too rigid to address", "start": 610.2, "duration": 6.12}, {"text": "the existing financing gaps in the", "start": 613.2, "duration": 7.02}, {"text": "programs we have for achieving sdgs", "start": 616.32, "duration": 6.3}, {"text": "we are committed to the principle of the", "start": 620.22, "duration": 5.76}, {"text": "U.N Charter and to a rules based", "start": 622.62, "duration": 5.159}, {"text": "International System", "start": 625.98, "duration": 4.26}, {"text": "so long as we have the power to change", "start": 627.779, "duration": 5.821}, {"text": "the rules that have worked against us", "start": 630.24, "duration": 6.599}, {"text": "and held us back", "start": 633.6, "duration": 7.44}, {"text": "in terms of our development for decades", "start": 636.839, "duration": 7.74}, {"text": "this is why Malawi strongly advocates", "start": 641.04, "duration": 7.739}, {"text": "for radical reform in the United Nations", "start": 644.579, "duration": 6.601}, {"text": "security Council itself", "start": 648.779, "duration": 5.461}, {"text": "whose various structure undermines the", "start": 651.18, "duration": 5.899}, {"text": "values of democracy inclusivity", "start": 654.24, "duration": 7.02}, {"text": "accountability and Trust", "start": 657.079, "duration": 6.221}, {"text": "it is no accident", "start": 661.26, "duration": 4.74}, {"text": "that at this 78th session of the United", "start": 663.3, "duration": 5.88}, {"text": "Nations General Assembly", "start": 666.0, "duration": 6.24}, {"text": "focused on rebuilding trust and", "start": 669.18, "duration": 5.099}, {"text": "solidarity", "start": 672.24, "duration": 4.32}, {"text": "only one head of state", "start": 674.279, "duration": 4.381}, {"text": "from the permanent members of the U.N", "start": 676.56, "duration": 5.3}, {"text": "security Council showed up", "start": 678.66, "duration": 3.2}, {"text": "that is not help", "start": 682.5, "duration": 4.68}, {"text": "you build trust", "start": 684.72, "duration": 6.54}, {"text": "that is not how you show solidarity", "start": 687.18, "duration": 6.659}, {"text": "that is not accountability", "start": 691.26, "duration": 5.639}, {"text": "that is not leadership", "start": 693.839, "duration": 5.521}, {"text": "as such I believe", "start": 696.899, "duration": 6.421}, {"text": "President Biden said it so well here", "start": 699.36, "duration": 7.08}, {"text": "and Malawi joins the United States", "start": 703.32, "duration": 6.84}, {"text": "in insisting that Africa must have a", "start": 706.44, "duration": 7.2}, {"text": "permanent assist on the U.N security", "start": 710.16, "duration": 6.54}, {"text": "Council with veto power", "start": 713.64, "duration": 5.4}, {"text": "because without that level of", "start": 716.7, "duration": 3.6}, {"text": "inclusivity", "start": 719.04, "duration": 4.2}, {"text": "rebuilding trust and reigniting Global", "start": 720.3, "duration": 6.979}, {"text": "solidarity will be a challenge", "start": 723.24, "duration": 4.039}, {"text": "one of the reasons we need a reformed", "start": 727.